WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.862
Four causal categories dominate the differential.

00:00:02.862 --> 00:00:06.200
Viral infections — led by Coxsackievirus, Parvovirus

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:09.538
B-nineteen, and SARS-CoV-2 — are the most

00:00:09.538 --> 00:00:10.015
common.

00:00:10.015 --> 00:00:13.354
Autoimmune disease, toxic exposures such as immune

00:00:13.354 --> 00:00:16.692
checkpoint inhibitors and anthracyclines, and rare post-vaccination

00:00:16.692 --> 00:00:18.600
cases complete the picture.
